    agy configure                    	Configure Antigravity CLI with some default values. But do not fully reset all other existing config values. ('aistack agy install' include configuration)
	agy info                            Print Antigravity CLI informations.
    agy show-config                  	Show current Antigravity CLI  configuration.
    agy reset                       	Reset all Antigravity CLI configuration.
	agy register <all|shell|vs>         Register Antigravity CLI PATH into shell env PATH ("all" supported shells or "bash", "zsh" or "fish") or into VS Code integrated terminal env PATH ("vs").
